              <h1>About Us</h1>
              <p>
                  LibHost is a revolutionary web platform, designed to seamlessly connect property owners across Liberia with travelers looking for short and long-term accommodations. We aim to transform the travel experience in Liberia, providing easy access to authentic and local stays while promoting local tourism.
              </p>
          </div>
